{"tid":202180,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"18-22 交心真心朋友 Whatsapp Group","createTime":"2017-04-15T10:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T08:29:34.000Z","uid":106244,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b8e5c3c59961dc23784f9e82eeaefb3ad40bd5d","tid":202180,"uid":106244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:09:20.000Z","msg":"一直係到尋找可以交心真心同玩得埋既好朋友<br />\n本身就無咩好傾得埋既朋友<br />\n小弟今年20 ，學生， 覺得年齡相近d 距離感會無甘大 所以定左係18-22<br />\n而地區係觀塘區 但係其實住邊都無所謂 不過係驚大家如果住太遠 出黎會唔方便<br />\n本身鍾意小貓三四隻既相處模式 所以暫時會將人數定為六人 因為通常一大班人 我總係存在感較低個個，TT 比較內向<br />\n希望入到群裡面既朋友可以積極健談d 同幼稚白痴d 都無所謂 <br />\n其實好羨慕日本 youtuber, fischer's 個種和洽 <br />\nP.s. 禁煙，少酒同盡量少粗口<br />\n如果你都係孤身一人既，點解我地唔一同前進?<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1GjVvrYRsIpuk83tPHQGTgewQZEOdyLdrgejVWavKaSE/prefill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1GjVvrYRsIpuk83tPHQGTgewQZEOdyLdrgejVWavKaSE%2Fprefill&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7173b918\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1GjVvrYRsIpuk83tPHQGTgewQZEOdyLdrgejVWavKaSE/prefill</a>"},{"pid":"ceb07326d4a937572f629ce2193de6a9222e9ab3","tid":202180,"uid":18286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"死番5p啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"440a79fc7070f8bbc54a96411ea6f73be93f07ec","tid":202180,"uid":30017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"咩link黎 google drive既？"},{"pid":"805491dfa4c7a780abb22a39efc28fdc2d53a472","tid":202180,"uid":106244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:19:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfCUMMf5LuuDIBWVOQPOnIf2m4b2lIoLG8VQgxjz5-28Reyyg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfCUMMf5LuuDIBWVOQPOnIf2m4b2lIoLG8VQgxjz5-28Reyyg%2Fviewform&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=acb8c0b3\" target=\"_blank\">https:/